#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Pariri Amministrattivi"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Qatt tħaddem fil-produzzjoni b'DEBUG attivat. Il-mod tal-debug jesponi "
"dettalji interni u stack traces."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Dejjem timplimenta Grylli wara proxy invers (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, jew Traefik)"
" u servu fuq HTTPS. Id-dejta sensittiva tal-utent trid tkun kriptata waqt "
"it-transitu."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Kun żgur li l-folder tad-dejta (database) huwa ssorveljat fuq l-host tiegħek"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Il-folder tal-uploadi huwa maqsum. Biex iżolat ir-riklami għal kull utent, "
"tikkonfigura d-direttorji u l-kontrolli tal-aċċess fil-livell tal-host."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Biex tirkupra backup: waqqaf il-kontenitur, ibdel id-data/grylli.db ma' "
"wieħed mill-folder tal-backups, u reġa' ibda l-kontenitur."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"L-amministraturi ma jistgħux ineħħu r-rwol tagħhom stess tal-amministratur "
"biex jipprevjenu lockout b'kumbinazzjoni."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Limiti ta' rati u lockouts awtomatikati tal-kontijiet huma infurzati biex "
"jipproteġu kontra attentati ta' login bil-forza bruta."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Passwords, kredenzjali tal-SMTP, u tokens tal-API huma kkripttati b'mod "
"kriptograffiku b'Fernet."

